  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Implement Placeholder Images for All Post Views\n\nEnsure all images throughout the application use placeholder images as fallbacks, with specific focus on fixing the error appearing in the single post view.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify the specific image error occurring in the single post view\n- Implement placeholder images for all image components in single post view\n- Audit all other post views (list view, grid view, card view, etc.) to ensure consistent placeholder usage\n- Add error handling for failed image loads with automatic fallback to placeholder\n- Ensure placeholder images are appropriately sized and styled for different contexts\n- Use a consistent placeholder image or loading state across the application\n- Handle edge cases: missing image URLs, broken URLs, slow-loading images\n- Verify no console errors appear when images fail to load\n- Test with posts that have no images, invalid image URLs, and valid images",
